OL,3,CITV Cymru Wales wins RTS award for
OL,4,C'gripping' Proud documentary
OL,6,FITV Cymru Wales has been recognised at
OL,7,Fthe 2026 Royal Television Society
OL,8,FAwards for its documentary Proud.
OL,10,FThe programme marked the fortieth
OL,11,Fanniversary of the first gay march in
OL,12,FWales, documenting the way society has
OL,13,Fchanged for the LGBTQ+ community since
OL,14,Fthen as well as the challenges which
OL,15,Fstill remain.
