OL,3,CITV Cymru Wales wins RTS award for
OL,4,C'gripping' Proud documentary
OL,6,FWithin its category Proud faced strong
OL,7,Fcompetition against the BBC North West
OL,8,Fprogramme How safe are our Nurseries?
OL,9,Fand the BBC Wales Investigates
OL,10,Fdocumentary, Unmasked: Extreme Far
OL,11,FRight.
OL,13,FPraising Proud for it's ability to
OL,14,Fconnect with the LGBTQ+ community,
OL,15,Fjudges said "in a category which
OL,16,Fincluded a number of impressive
OL,17,Finvestigations, the judges chose a
OL,18,Fprogramme they found gripping and
OL,19,Fauthentic.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
