OL,3,CITV Cymru Wales wins RTS award for
OL,4,C'gripping' Proud documentary
OL,6,F"The team were praised for the way
OL,7,Fthis documentary had given a voice to
OL,8,Findividuals in the community, and one
OL,9,Fjudge commented that it was a film
OL,10,Feveryone should find time to watch."
OL,12,FCommenting on the RTS win, Programme
OL,13,FProducer and Director, Nicola Hendy
OL,14,Fsays even though Proud looks back 40
OL,15,Fyears since the first gay pride march
OL,16,Fin Wales, it still remains relevant
OL,17,Ftoday.
OL,19,F"As an almost forty-year-old gay woman
OL,20,Fthis story resonated hugely with me.
OL,26,@rD@dO]
