OL,3,CITV Cymru Wales wins RTS award for
OL,4,C'gripping' Proud documentary
OL,6,F"If we needed a reminder of why this
OL,7,Ftopic is so important today -whilst we
OL,8,Fwere making the programme Hungary
OL,9,Fannounced it was banning all pride
OL,10,Fmarches - showing how the freedoms we
OL,11,Fhave right now, can be taken away.
OL,13,F"I'm so grateful to everyone who
OL,14,Fshared their experiences with us for
OL,15,Fthe programme. For the battles they
OL,16,Ffought so that people like me can be
OL,17,Ffree to marry the person I love.
