OL,3,CITV Cymru Wales wins RTS award for
OL,4,C'gripping' Proud documentary
OL,6,F"I'm also grateful to ITV Cymru Wales
OL,7,Ffor championing this project, and
OL,8,Fgiving us the space to tell people's
OL,9,Fstories."
OL,11,FIn 1985 those who were homosexual had
OL,12,Fno rights in law. That was despite
OL,13,Fhomosexuality being decriminalised in
OL,14,F1967 in the UK.
OL,16,FPeople could still be arrested for
OL,17,Fbeing gay and lose custody of their
OL,18,Fchildren, so being visible wasn't
OL,19,Falways easy.
