OL,3,CITV Cymru Wales wins RTS award for
OL,4,C'gripping' Proud documentary
OL,6,FIt was against this backdrop that
OL,7,FWales had its first ever gay march,
OL,8,Forganised by a small group of students
OL,9,Fat Cardiff University's Gay Society.
OL,11,FFrancis Brown was one of the people
OL,12,Finvolved and describes the initial
OL,13,Freaction to the idea:
OL,15,F"We thought, really?! This was
OL,16,FCardiff, not London or New York or San
OL,17,FFrancisco, and there had been nothing
OL,18,Flike this before.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
