OL,3,CITV Cymru Wales wins RTS award for
OL,4,C'gripping' Proud documentary
OL,6,F"We contacted the police, we got
OL,7,Fpermission, and then we tried to get
OL,8,Fpeople to come along."
OL,10,FThe march itself was relatively small.
OL,11,FActivists held placards and chanted
OL,12,Fthings like "2, 4,6 ,8, is that copper
OL,13,Freally straight."
OL,15,FDespite it being small it started a
OL,16,Fmovement that still continues today.
